_:N6330443cf0e942b3a21a390cdae54edd <http://schema.org/description> "The Leasehold Advisory Service (LEASE) gives free legal advice to leaseholders on the law affecting residential leasehold in England and Wales. LEASE is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government ." .
